					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610225333" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;" >sirpudding</a></span> <span class="odate time_1447117551 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">10 Nov 2015 01:05</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2405025">
									

<p>The whole &quot;Is this the end of <em>Chinatown</em> or the beginning of the third act of <em>Lethal Weapon</em>?&quot; thing is less obvious without it. What <em>are</em> these two hard-boiled occult investigators going to do with their administrative leave?</p>

