<p>Psul's intent was to leave this ambiguous.</p>
<p>I think that certainly Griffiths thought they might go off the reservation, if given leave under these circumstances and benched them anyway, whether that is cynical CYA, tacit approval, or a setup is ambiguous. I think that these two guys probably thought about trying to save her, and maybe they did try, and maybe they even succeeded. If something like that did officially did not happen, there would never be a report about it.</p>

